; Connect Ethernet launcher - one-click auto-connect via IconX.
; AUTO/CLOSE (no WAIT): the window auto-closes on success; on failure
; NetworkConfig.rexx pops a requester with the reason before exiting.
; CON title must stay space-free or AmigaDOS truncates the redirect target.
SYS:Rexxc/rx >CON:0/20/680/400/Connect-Ethernet/AUTO/CLOSE s:NetworkConfig.rexx ONLINE ETHERNET
